  </section>

  <section class="llc-card-highlight space-y-4 !p-6 sm:!p-8">
    <p class="llc-helper">Bottom line</p>
    <h2>Our final recommendation</h2>
    <p class="llc-section-copy text-slate-700">
      If you want the safest paid default, start with {defaultPick.name}. If you care most about
      the cheapest viable year-one cost, {cheapestViablePick.name} is the budget pick to compare
      next. The provider we would steer most first-time founders away from is {avoidPick?.name},
      because the markup is too hard to justify for a standard LLC filing.
    </p>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500">
      Affiliate disclosure: LLCAtlas is reader-supported. When you buy through our links, we may
      earn a commission. That does not change our rankings.
    </p>
